Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Friday and welcome back to our 135th Weekly Dose of Optimism. Packy i=
s on his way back from a busy couple of days down in Austin, Texas -- word =
on the street is he's started lifting shirtless and joined a few Mastermind=
s already. You can take the man out of Austin but it's really hard to take =
a few days of Austin out of the man, ya know? But the fun for Packy is just=
 getting started -- the old man is hosting my bachelor party in NYC this we=
ekend. Let's see if he can keep up. If you see us around town Friday or Sat=
urday night...you didn't =F0=9F=A4=9D.
Let's get to it.=20
